{
  "texts": [
    "The following list summarizes the different components, which are discussed in more depth in the indicated sub-sections.",
    "Communication/User Interface: This is the primary touchpoint for the user, allowing them to pose questions either through natural language or by using UI elements.",
    "Postcomputation, this component also converts the retrieved answer into a format that is easily comprehensible to the user.",
    "(See Sect. 5.1) 2.",
    "Input Understanding: Here, the user's query undergoes translation into a machine-readable format."
  ]
}